Name: AI: Rampage
About the game: Tactical stealth action in a post-apocalyptic settings! Fight against the robots and reclaim the land! Attempt to survive in a post-apocalyptic wasteland, where it seems like everything wants you dead! Features: Stealth Action! Intelligent enemy AI includes visibility and audibility parameters The use of many of the game's vehicles Futuristic weapons and items - Frickin' Lasers, invisibility cloaking devices and holograms! When, finally, the dust of the battle settles, who will stand victorious? Complex intelligence, durability and brute force, or human ingenuity? The choice is yours.
